JSP scripting elements:
1. JSP exression: syntax:     <%=some java epression %>
ex: the time on the server is <%= new java.util.Date() %>
 To upper case <%= new String("Hello J").toUpper() %>

2. JSP sciptlet:    <% some java code: 1 to many lines %>.
Inser 1 to many lines of Java code.
to include content in the page use: out.println()


3. JSP Declaration:   <%! variables or method declaration %>
we can declare a method in the jsp
call method n the same jsp


